Class BaseApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.amelia.foundation.BaseApplication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParcelInterface, ParcelReceiver, RegistrarBase, VendorRegistrar, ExceptionRegistrar
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultApplication, MinimalApplication

    public abstract class BaseApplication
extends java.lang.Object
implements VendorRegistrar, ExceptionRegistrar, ParcelInterface, ParcelReceiver
    When a BaseApplication is instigated, its main thread is dedicated to running the Looper that takes care of managing the top-level application tasks and parcels.
